HONECKER, MARGOT; KRENZ, EGON; EAST GERMANY -- EMIGRATION; KOHL, HELMUT; 
MITTERRAND, FRANCOIS; FRANCE -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY 
