<P>
Mary Jane Visser testified in Lincoln, Neb., that she took confidential 
information on athletes from the University of Nebraska files before she was 
fired as an adviser. 
</P>
<P>
Visser, who claims she was fired because she was investigating student 
athletes' records, told a U.S. District Court jury that she began keeping track 
